data.description: Nestle in beautiful Cape Coral, this inviting 3 bedroom, 2-bath home with spacious 2-car garage is a true gem.  Step inside to discover a spacious and inviting interior that welcomes you home.  The open floor plan connects the living room, dining area and kitchen, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The fully fenced backyard is an outdoor paradise. with a fantastic patio with an outdoor kitchen, its the idea spot for entertaining, barbecues or simply relaxing . Surrounded by new homes in a vibrant community, this property offers the perfect bland of comfort, modern living and the convenience of an easy access to shopping centers, restaurants and entertainment. Plus home is walking distance to the New- Gator Trails Park , park offers picnic shelters with BBQ Grills, fitness stations, playground equipment, multi-use path and restrooms.  Schedule your showing today, owner is ready to sell.  Updates on the home- New Rood 2023, fence 2023, living room laminate floors 2020, laminate floors bedroom 2022. The appliances are newer the fridge, stove and microwave. The washer,  dryer, Paradise grill -propane and shed are included.
